QuestData.Title: A Rousing Aroma
QuestData.Description: <Sabina is unresponsive. Her exposed flesh cracked and blistered. Perhaps something with a pungent aroma will rouse her.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect $1oa Pungent Swarmer Toxin from Ravenous Swarms.
QuestData.RewardText:
<Sabina begins to stir. >
Are... are they back? Help... help me.
